^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now, let's discuss Hope's trump play. She made the correct play. Had she more entries, she can afford to cash the A or K first, but she doesn't. But given I preempted, it is much more likely hearts are split 3-1 with Kerrie having 3. So, her play is the correct one even though it happened to fail here. It will be right most of the time. You can't worry about a play that fails if it is the right play. In the long run you will come out way ahead.|
