^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Although it occurs rarely, 2N has the same meaning with or without the 1S overcall. One other good rule of thumb. If you are not sure what a bid means, assume the strongest reasonable meaning and bid accordingly. So, on this hand, if not sure, you should have still assumed the 2N was 18-19, just in case. |
