^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|In general, if you are not sure if a bid is forcing or not, assume it is forcing. It will work out more often than not (even when the bid was not meant to be forcing). 3N should make on the hand as long as you attack diamonds. You should take 3 diamonds, 3 clubs, and can easily come to at least 3 tricks in the majors.|
